<div class="container pt-5">
  <div class="page-tittle text-center">
    問い合わせ情報入力
  </div>

 <div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex align-self-center justify-content-lg-end">
    名前
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
    <%= @customer.name %>
   </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex align-self-center justify-content-lg-end">
    電話番号
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
    <%= @customer.telephone_number %>
   </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex align-self-center justify-content-lg-end">
    メールアドレス
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
    <%= @customer.email %>
   </div>
  </div>

  <%= form_with model: @enquiry, url: customer_enquiries_path, method: :post do |f| %>
    <div class="row">
     <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex justify-content-lg-end">
      問い合わせ内容
     </div>
     <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
      <%= f.text_area :content, :placeholder => "必須(1～200文字まで)", cols: "38",rows: "8" %>
     </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row confirm-text p-1 align-items-center justify-content-center text-center">
   <div class="col-12">
   <i class="far fa-paper-plane"></i>
   こちらの情報を下記リフォーム会社へ送信します
   <i class="far fa-paper-plane"></i>
   </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex align-self-center justify-content-lg-end">
    会社名
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
    <%= @manager.name %>
   </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex align-self-center justify-content-lg-end">
    住所
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
    <%= @manager.address %>
   </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex align-self-center justify-content-lg-end">
    電話番号
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
    <%= @manager.telephone_number %>
   </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-lg-4 item-tittle d-flex align-self-center justify-content-lg-end">
    メールアドレス
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-8 text align-self-center">
    <%= @manager.email %>
   </div>
  </div>

 <div class="row mt-3 mb-3">
   <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
    <div class="enquiry-message">
      問い合わせ完了後、上記会社よりお電話またはメールがございますので
      ご連絡をお待ちください<br>
      定休日の関係でご連絡が遅くなる場合もございますのでご了承下さい<br>
      問い合わせ完了後は、マイページ→問い合わせ一覧より詳細が確認できます
    </div>
  </div>
 </div>

  <div class="row mb-3 mt-3 text-center">
   <div class="col-lg-6 col-5">
    <%= link_to "部屋詳細に戻る", customer_room_path(@room.id), data: {confirm: "入力情報が消えてしまいます。戻りますか？"}, class: "btn" %>
   </div>
   <div class="col-lg-6 col-7">
    <%= f.hidden_field :manager_id, :value => @manager.id %>
    <%= f.hidden_field :room_id, :value => @room.id %>
    <%= f.hidden_field :customer_id, :value => @customer.id %>
    <%= f.submit "問い合わせを完了する", class: "submitButton", onclick: "return confirm('本当に完了しますか？')" %>
    </div>
  </div>
 <% end %>

 </div>
 </div>

</div>